and be with them.

796
00:43:24,394 --> 00:43:28,331
- Be family.

797
00:43:33,028 --> 00:43:36,965
I also have this nephew.

798
00:43:39,659 --> 00:43:42,204
He screws up
once and again.

799
00:43:42,329 --> 00:43:44,747
One mistake after the other
and...

800
00:43:44,873 --> 00:43:47,309
But he's a grown up.

801
00:43:47,334 --> 00:43:50,628
I can't treat him
like a child.

802
00:43:50,753 --> 00:43:54,841
What do you do
in that case?

803
00:43:54,966 --> 00:43:57,886
I get you
perfectly well.

804
00:43:58,011 --> 00:44:00,013
I know what you're
talking about.

805
00:44:00,138 --> 00:44:02,324
Nobody said it'd be easy.

806
00:44:02,349 --> 00:44:03,866
All you can do

807
00:44:03,892 --> 00:44:07,870
is always stay alert.

808
00:44:07,896 --> 00:44:12,250
What do you exactly mean?

809
00:44:12,275 --> 00:44:13,669
Always be with them.

810
00:44:13,693 --> 00:44:15,253
Be by their side

811
00:44:15,278 --> 00:44:17,072
in good and bad
times.

812
00:44:17,197 --> 00:44:22,035
Stand, help,
give good advice.

813
00:44:22,160 --> 00:44:25,138
Be always there.

814
00:44:57,862 --> 00:45:01,883
José!

815
00:45:01,908 --> 00:45:03,552
José, open up!

816
00:45:03,577 --> 00:45:06,513
I just want to talk to you.

817
00:45:41,490 --> 00:45:43,508
José.

818
00:46:03,512 --> 00:46:06,531
José.

819
00:46:06,556 --> 00:46:09,534
José, wake up.

820
00:46:12,020 --> 00:46:14,856
José,
I want to talk.

